title: [Vornavis, Peasant Holdings]
description: A faint breeze rustles the hundreds of apple branches populating the orchard.  Dark shadows dart in and out of the trees, hiding in the gloom before you catch a glimpse of what they might be.  A strange leathery flapping sound seems to emanate from all around.
paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, east, southeast, south, southwest, west, northwest
